343464961.name: Hidden Fates
343464961.description: A wild set loaded with all-time favorites, the Pokémon TCG: Hidden Fates expansion is a collector’s dream and a player’s paradise! Soar to new heights with the first TAG TEAM trio, Moltres & Zapdos & Articuno-GX, as well as Gyarados-GX and more than 75 Pokémon in their Shiny forms—including Mewtwo-GX and Charizard-GX! Reach out for the unusual, astonishing power of Pokémon, and discover your own Hidden Fates!

343464962.name: Hidden Fates

F19TinCharizardGXBundle.name: Charizard-GX Deck
F19TinCharizardGXBundle.description: Refuel that fire! Keep recycling Energy to power up massive attacks with Charizard-GX, Arcanine, and Salazzle in this Fire-type deck.

F19TinGarchompGiratinaGXBundle.name: Garchomp & Giratina-GX Deck
F19TinGarchompGiratinaGXBundle.description: Ghostly tricks and draconic determination! Damage your opponent’s Bench while protecting your own with Garchomp & Giratina-GX, Gengar, and Mew in this Psychic- and Fighting-type deck.

F19TinGyaradosGXBundle.name: Gyarados-GX Deck
F19TinGyaradosGXBundle.description: A storm surge of destruction! Use the waves to your advantage and move Energy around where you need it with Gyarados-GX, Articuno, and Naganadel in this Water-type deck.

F19TinLucarioMelmetalGXBundle.name: Lucario & Melmetal-GX Deck
F19TinLucarioMelmetalGXBundle.description: Put the pedal to the metal! Build up an impenetrable wall and keep it fortified with Lucario & Melmetal-GX, Magnezone, and Pidgeotto in this Metal-type deck.

F19TinMewtwoMewGXBundle.name: Mewtwo & Mew-GX Deck
F19TinMewtwoMewGXBundle.description: Two minds are better than one! Do massive damage and keep your own team in fighting shape with Mewtwo & Mew-GX, Malamar, and Blissey in this Psychic-type deck.

F19TinRaichuGXBundle.name: Raichu-GX Deck
F19TinRaichuGXBundle.description: Maximum voltage incoming! Keep the electricity flowing to your Pokémon with Raichu-GX, Magnezone, and Zebstrika in this Lightning-type deck.
